Taking inspiration from the Futuro Houses by Matti Suuronen that were built through the 1960’s and 70’s. A time when exploration of space was at an all-time high along with an increase in leisure time. Helio House follows the same ideology — a retro-futuristic space designed for relaxation.
Inside the house, the main floor includes two bedrooms and a lounge area. The lower floor is accessed by a hidden lift and houses a bathroom and storage space.
Built in Unreal Engine 5, the space comes with a downloadable program which allows the viewer to explore the interior and the surrounding area.', 72, '75d93a33-fb5f-4126-99bd-e3c4d4d197ad', 'gid://shopify/Product/8302965653791', '4e08b85d-c92c-4b20-b077-12867ace8e92', 4500, 'ms://seo/product/joe_mortell-10:00_pm', true);
